# MCP Server Integrations

## Available MCP Servers

### E-commerce & Fulfillment
- **shopify**: Product management, orders
- **pictorem**: Print-on-demand services
- **stripe**: Payment processing
- **shipstation**: Shipping management

### Marketing & Analytics
- **facebook-ads**: Ad campaigns
- **instagram-api**: Content posting
- **pinterest-api**: Pin management
- **google-analytics**: Web analytics
- **mailchimp**: Email marketing

### Data & Storage
- **supabase**: Primary database
- **neo4j**: Graph relationships
- **cloudinary**: Media storage
- **s3**: File storage

### AI & Processing
- **openai**: Language models
- **anthropic**: Claude integration
- **stability**: Image generation
- **replicate**: Model hosting

### Communication
- **slack**: Team notifications
- **email**: Customer communication
- **sms**: Alerts and updates
- **webhook**: External integrations

## Integration Patterns

### Authentication
```javascript
// MCP client credentials
{
  "id": "unique-id",
  "name": "Service Name",
  "authType": "oauth2|apiKey",
  "credentials": {
    // Service-specific auth
  }
}
```

### Error Handling
```javascript
try {
  // MCP operation
} catch (error) {
  if (error.code === 'RATE_LIMIT') {
    // Implement backoff
  } else if (error.code === 'AUTH_FAILED') {
    // Refresh credentials
  } else {
    // Generic error handling
  }
}
```

### Data Transformation
- Input validation
- Format standardization
- Output mapping
- Type checking

## Best Practices
1. Cache frequently used data
2. Batch operations when possible
3. Implement retry logic
4. Monitor API quotas
5. Log all interactions

# Inter-Agent Communication

## Communication Patterns

### 1. Direct Workflow Execution
```javascript
// Parent agent calling child
{
  "node": "toolWorkflow",
  "parameters": {
    "workflowId": "childAgentId",
    "workflowInputs": {
      "trigger_conditions": "specific_task",
      "data": {}
    }
  }
}
```

### 2. Webhook Communication
```javascript
// Async communication
{
  "method": "POST",
  "url": "{{baseUrl}}/webhook/agent-name",
  "headers": {
    "Content-Type": "application/json"
  },
  "body": {
    "trigger_conditions": "task",
    "priority": "high",
    "callback_url": "{{responseUrl}}"
  }
}
```

### 3. Event-Driven
```javascript
// Pub/sub pattern
{
  "event": "order.created",
  "subscribers": [
    "fulfillment-agent",
    "email-agent",
    "analytics-agent"
  ]
}
```

## Data Flow Standards

### Request Format
```json
{
  "source_agent": "marketing_director",
  "target_agent": "content_strategy",
  "trigger_conditions": "create_campaign",
  "priority": "high",
  "data": {
    "campaign_type": "seasonal",
    "budget": 5000,
    "timeline": "2_weeks"
  },
  "metadata": {
    "request_id": "uuid",
    "timestamp": "ISO8601",
    "correlation_id": "uuid"
  }
}
```

### Response Format
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "source_agent": "content_strategy",
  "data": {
    "campaign_id": "uuid",
    "deliverables": [],
    "timeline": {}
  },
  "metadata": {
    "response_id": "uuid",
    "request_id": "uuid",
    "processing_time_ms": 1234
  }
}
```

## Coordination Protocols

### Sequential Processing
- Ordered task execution
- Dependency management
- Result aggregation

### Parallel Processing
- Concurrent execution
- Result merging
- Conflict resolution

### Hierarchical Delegation
- Top-down task assignment
- Bottom-up reporting
- Escalation paths

# Agent Workflow Examples

## Marketing Director Agent
```json
{
  "trigger_conditions": "quarterly_planning",
  "data": {
    "quarter": "Q2_2024",
    "budget": 50000,
    "goals": {
      "revenue_target": 500000,
      "new_customers": 1000,
      "brand_awareness": "+20%"
    }
  }
}

// Expected Response
{
  "status": "success",
  "plan": {
    "campaigns": [
      {
        "name": "Spring Art Collection",
        "budget": 20000,
        "channels": ["social", "email", "paid"]
      }
    ],
    "resource_allocation": {
      "content_team": "40%",
      "paid_media": "35%",
      "social_media": "25%"
    }
  }
}
```

## Content Strategy Agent
```json
{
  "trigger_conditions": "content_calendar",
  "data": {
    "period": "march_2024",
    "themes": ["spring_refresh", "artist_spotlight"],
    "content_types": ["blog", "social", "email"]
  }
}

// Expected Response
{
  "status": "success",
  "calendar": {
    "week_1": [
      {
        "date": "2024-03-01",
        "type": "blog",
        "title": "5 Ways to Refresh Your Space",
        "platforms": ["website", "email"]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

## Social Media Director
```json
{
  "trigger_conditions": "campaign_social",
  "data": {
    "campaign_id": "spring_2024",
    "platforms": ["instagram", "facebook", "pinterest"],
    "content_count": 30,
    "timeline": "4_weeks"
  }
}

// Expected Response
{
  "status": "success",
  "social_plan": {
    "instagram": {
      "posts": 10,
      "stories": 20,
      "reels": 5
    },
    "facebook": {
      "posts": 8,
      "ads": 5
    },
    "pinterest": {
      "pins": 15,
      "boards": 2
    }
  }
}
```

## Common Patterns

### Error Response
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "error": {
    "code": "VALIDATION_ERROR",
    "message": "Missing required field: campaign_id",
    "details": {
      "field": "campaign_id",
      "requirement": "string, required"
    }
  },
  "timestamp": "2024-03-15T10:30:00Z"
}
```

### Async Processing
```json
{
  "status": "accepted",
  "job_id": "job_123456",
  "estimated_completion": "2024-03-15T11:00:00Z",
  "status_url": "/status/job_123456"
}
```
